                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/7389" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1160</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">7421 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">实体企业金融化，云南白药路在何方？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">After the financialization of entity enterprises,What should Yunnan Baiyao do in the future？</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">徐秀红，王新蕾，冯慧，阮心怡，段哲希，李秀珠</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">福建农林大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药集团股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">医药卫生工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">17 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">云南白药；实体企业；金融化</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Yunnan Baiyao; Entity enterprise; Financialization</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">随着市场需求的不断下降，我国实体经济出现产能过剩的现象，大量资本涌入金融市场，虚拟经济得到高速发展，促进了实体企业的金融化。为此“二十大”报告指出要坚持把发展经济的着力点放在实体经济上。云南白药作为传统百年中药老字号，金融化水平却不断上升，2019年更是投资百亿入局股票市场，经历从2020年年赚26亿到2021年第三季度亏损15亿，业绩变化速度之快，令人叹为观止。本案例以云南白药一系列的金融化举动为主线，分析云南白药金融化的特征、动因、对主业发展的影响等，旨在引导学员运用相关理论分析企业选择金融化应该注意的事项，以及如何协调好金融化程度和发展主业的关系，以保证企业的持续健康发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">With the continuous decline of market demand, China&#39;s real economy has experienced overcapacity, and a large amount of capital has flooded into the financial market. The virtual economy has developed rapidly, promoted the financialization of entity enterprises. Therefore, the report of the 20th National Congress of the Communist Party of China pointed out that the focus of economic development should be on the real economy. Yunnan Baiyao, as a traditional and time-honored brand of traditional Chinese medicine with a history of over one hundred years, has continuously increased its level of financialization. In 2019, it invested more than ten billions of yuan in the stock market. It experienced ranges from an annual profit of 2.6 billion in 2020 to a loss of 1.5 billion in the third quarter of 2021, and the speed of performance change is astonishing. This case focuses on a series of financialization actions of Yunnan Baiyao, analyzing the characteristics, motivations, and impact on the development of its main business, aiming to guide students to use relevant theories to analyze the matters that enterprises should pay attention to when choosing financialization, as well as how to coordinate the relationship between the degree of financialization and the development of the main business, in order to ensure the sustainable and healthy development of the enterprise.</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2021</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理理论与实务》、《企业战略管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">实体企业金融化的含义及特征；多元化经营理论；现金管理动机；蓄水池效应；挤出效应；资产配置理论</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2023-07</td>
                            </tr>
